{
  "texts": [
    "Moreover, we designed a hybrid tractography pipeline capable of combining anatomical constraints and diffusion signal from the lesioned tissue.",
    "Finally, we use the reconstructed networks before and after brain surgery to train a machine learning model able to extract information about non-normative patterns of structural reorganization.",
    "We also set out to determine whether functional activity was present within the brain tumor.",
    "We find qualitatively similar signals between healthy and tumor tissues.",
    "However, the fact that there is a non-zero tumor functional signal is not indicative of its relevance."
  ]
}